{"Version": "1.0.0", "LINES": [{"text": "Orange juice is a several\nbillion dollar industry.", "start": 5.04, "duration": 3.12, "ents": [{"label_": "MONEY", "text": "several\nbillion dollar"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Here, on almost 600,000\nhectares of land, oranges are grown", "start": 13.32, "duration": 5.12, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "almost 600,000"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Like any other day, he has\neight hours of work ahead of him.", "start": 90.4, "duration": 3.76, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "eight hours"}], "sentiment": -0.125}, {"text": "This canister holds\n5 liters of water.", "start": 99.16, "duration": 2.84, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "I need two of these canisters\nto get through the day.", "start": 105.6, "duration": 3.32, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "the day"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "You drink ten\nliters a day?", "start": 109.32, "duration": 2.56, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "ten"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Temperatures on the plantations can\nreach up to 35 degrees celsius.", "start": 116.56, "duration": 4.8, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "35 degrees"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "For 6 years, Afonso\nhas been picking oranges", "start": 125.92, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "6 years"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Afonso"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In a good month, he\nearns about 250 euros.", "start": 131.2, "duration": 3.6, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "a good month"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "about 250"}], "sentiment": 0.7}, {"text": "A bag weighs\n27 kilos.", "start": 196.48, "duration": 2.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "27"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Just around 5,000\npeople normally live here.", "start": 237.36, "duration": 2.84, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "5,000"}], "sentiment": 0.13636363636363635}, {"text": "But between May and December\nthat number can grow to 6,000.", "start": 241.48, "duration": 3.72, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "May"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "December"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "6,000"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "some 2,000\nkilometers away,", "start": 259.12, "duration": 1.72, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "some 2,000"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "To reach the plantations, Afonso\nhas to travel by bus for 45 minutes.", "start": 278.36, "duration": 5.08, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Afonso"}, {"label_": "TIME", "text": "45 minutes"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Afonso is banned from\nworking for eleven days,", "start": 361.64, "duration": 3.24, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Afonso"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "eleven days"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Around 75% of the world's orange\njuice exports come from the country.", "start": 422.76, "duration": 4.36, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "Around 75%"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "To make it, workers pick between 65", "start": 427.2, "duration": 2.76, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "and 110 billion\noranges a year, by hand.", "start": 430.04, "duration": 4.08, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "110 billion"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "a year"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The industry is dominated by\nthree multinational companies,", "start": 434.12, "duration": 3.68, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "on the plantation of\none of their suppliers.", "start": 477.0, "duration": 2.84, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The green chlorophyll in the peel only\nbreaks down below 12 degrees Celsius,", "start": 493.84, "duration": 4.8, "ents": [], "sentiment": -0.11851851851851854}, {"text": "In this field, 30 workers pick\noranges for consumption in Brazil", "start": 503.4, "duration": 4.04, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "30"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Brazil"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "which are up to\nfive meters tall.", "start": 521.24, "duration": 2.12, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "five meters"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "A filled sack weighs\nabout 27 kilos.", "start": 524.16, "duration": 3.44, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "about 27"}], "sentiment": 0.4}, {"text": "Now I know that you work the\ntree from top to bottom in one go.", "start": 537.44, "duration": 3.44, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "With their bare hands, each\nof them harvests about 1.6 tons", "start": 563.04, "duration": 4.36, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "about 1.6 tons"}], "sentiment": 0.05}, {"text": "So on average, each one fills just\nunder eight 27-kilo bags per hour", "start": 569.96, "duration": 5.48, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "27-kilo"}], "sentiment": -0.15}, {"text": "they have to harvest\nan average of 60 bags.", "start": 613.56, "duration": 2.8, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "60"}], "sentiment": -0.15}, {"text": "The billion-dollar juice companies pay\nthe legal minimum wage of 1,200 reais,", "start": 627.96, "duration": 4.88, "ents": [{"label_": "MONEY", "text": "billion-dollar"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "1,200"}], "sentiment": 0.2}, {"text": "the equivalent of around\n200 euros a month,", "start": 632.92, "duration": 2.8, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "a month"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "the association of\nthe three juice giants.", "start": 657.84, "duration": 2.76, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "This increases an average\nsalary to about 280 euros.", "start": 668.48, "duration": 4.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "about 280"}], "sentiment": -0.15}, {"text": "The 70 year-old\nhas dedicated his life", "start": 775.04, "duration": 3.08, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "70 year-old"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "He was head of the\nFeraesp union until 2017.", "start": 781.0, "duration": 4.36, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2017"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Companies have been allowed\nto outsource work since 2017.", "start": 820.44, "duration": 3.56, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2017"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "for it to third parties\n? including individuals.", "start": 829.92, "duration": 3.0, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "third"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "As outsourcing has\ngrown since 2017,", "start": 850.52, "duration": 3.84, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2017"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "We always find violations when\nthird-party companies are involved.", "start": 867.76, "duration": 4.16, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "for 25 years, including\non orange plantations.", "start": 888.28, "duration": 4.16, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "25 years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In the last seven years, the\nMinistry of Labor in Sao Paulo", "start": 916.72, "duration": 3.6, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the last seven years"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "the\nMinistry of Labor"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Sao Paulo"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "has recorded over\n1,300 violations.", "start": 920.32, "duration": 2.24, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "1,300"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "50,000 people work\nin the fields every year", "start": 1025.76, "duration": 3.36, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "50,000"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "every year"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "we discovered a group of\nabout 37 workers.", "start": 1078.32, "duration": 3.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "about 37"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "These images show footage from\n2020 by Swiss NGO Public Eye:", "start": 1107.64, "duration": 5.04, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2020"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Swiss NGO Public Eye"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "He forwards us a voice\nmessage from one of his clients.", "start": 1242.6, "duration": 3.48, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "My name is Irani Biazotti, I worked\nas an orange farmer for 30 years.", "start": 1328.44, "duration": 6.4, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Irani Biazotti"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "30 years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "On his 60 hectares of\nland, he farmed oranges,", "start": 1346.28, "duration": 3.68, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "60 hectares"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "which he sold to Cutrale and\nCitrosuco, two major citrus exporters.", "start": 1349.96, "duration": 5.0, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "Cutrale"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Citrosuco"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}], "sentiment": 0.0625}, {"text": "For 30 years I worked in the\nfields with love and dedication,", "start": 1385.32, "duration": 3.84, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "30 years"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "Biazotti is 75, and it will take\nhim at least four more years,", "start": 1397.24, "duration": 3.88, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "Biazotti"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "75"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "at least four"}], "sentiment": 0.1}, {"text": "more than 1,500 former farmers\nare suing for financial compensation.", "start": 1412.48, "duration": 5.0, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "more than 1,500"}], "sentiment": 0.16666666666666666}, {"text": "in 2016.", "start": 1437.68, "duration": 1.52, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2016"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "against one of\nthe big companies.", "start": 1443.72, "duration": 2.12, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "for 27 years, having come here\nfrom northeastern Brazil as a child.", "start": 1454.44, "duration": 4.24, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "27 years"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Brazil"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "She earns between 180 and 280 euros a\nmonth,", "start": 1480.6, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "between 180 and"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "280"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "a\nmonth"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Since 2018, I\u2019m\nlonger the same.", "start": 1490.84, "duration": 3.28, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2018"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "and their 21-year-old\ndaughter recently started too.", "start": 1511.96, "duration": 2.68, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "21-year-old"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Since 2018, Vitoria has\nhad to take daily medication", "start": 1553.2, "duration": 4.08, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2018"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Vitoria"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "daily"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "one person dies every 2 days\nin Brazil from pesticide poisoning.", "start": 1640.84, "duration": 7.56, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "2 days"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Brazil"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 2019, she decided\nto take her case to court.", "start": 1663.76, "duration": 3.56, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2019"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "and the juice industry in 1977 to help\nmake citrus farming more sustainable.", "start": 1776.92, "duration": 5.76, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1977"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "She has been researching agrochemical\nuse in Brazil for 12 years.", "start": 1882.92, "duration": 4.12, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Brazil"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "12 years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 2017, she published her\nfindings in her home country.", "start": 1887.16, "duration": 4.32, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2017"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "56,000 cases of pesticide poisoning\nwere reported between 2010 and 2019.", "start": 1898.8, "duration": 5.96, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "56,000"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "between 2010 and 2019"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "That's an average\nof 10 per day,", "start": 1904.76, "duration": 2.8, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "10 per day"}], "sentiment": -0.15}, {"text": "but the ministry calculates that for\nevery case reported, 50 go undetected.", "start": 1907.56, "duration": 4.76, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "50"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "That means that we may have 2\nmillion sick and poisoned people.", "start": 1912.4, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "MONEY", "text": "2\nmillion"}], "sentiment": -0.7142857142857143}, {"text": "There are 116 pesticides approved\nfor citrus cultivation in Brazil,", "start": 1970.16, "duration": 4.64, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "116"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Brazil"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "and over 30 of them\nare banned in the EU.", "start": 1974.84, "duration": 3.12, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "over 30"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "EU"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Yet 10% of these banned chemicals are\nsold to Brazil by companies in Europe.", "start": 1977.96, "duration": 4.8, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "10%"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Brazil"}, {"label_": "LOC", "text": "Europe"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Europe is one of the biggest\nconsumers of Brazilian products.", "start": 2011.96, "duration": 3.28, "ents": [{"label_": "LOC", "text": "Europe"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "Brazilian"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 2018, the European\nFood Safety Authority", "start": 2018.88, "duration": 3.24, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2018"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "European"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "About 7% had pesticide residues\nabove the EU's approved limit.", "start": 2026.32, "duration": 5.04, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "About 7%"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "EU"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 2019, Larissa Mies Bombardi decided\nto publish her studies in Europe.", "start": 2032.6, "duration": 5.84, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2019"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Larissa Mies Bombardi"}, {"label_": "LOC", "text": "Europe"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "the more time passed, the more she\nfeared for herself and her two sons.", "start": 2066.92, "duration": 4.48, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "In early 2021, Bombardi left\nBrazil and moved to Belgium.", "start": 2072.92, "duration": 4.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "early 2021"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Bombardi"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Brazil"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Belgium"}], "sentiment": 0.05}, {"text": "Ethics should come first and\nforemost above economic interest.", "start": 2087.48, "duration": 4.44, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}], "sentiment": 0.15}, {"text": "that feeds on\none of the pests.", "start": 2135.8, "duration": 2.0, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "We produce about\n100,000 tamarixia a month", "start": 2144.56, "duration": 4.96, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "about\n100,000"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "to cut down pesticide use by\n50% compared to 20 years ago.", "start": 2158.92, "duration": 3.64, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "50%"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "20 years ago"}], "sentiment": -0.15555555555555559}, {"text": "A plant that currently\nproduces 200 kilos of oranges", "start": 2174.32, "duration": 3.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "200"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "would then only\nyield 10 kilos.", "start": 2177.68, "duration": 2.84, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "10"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "has grown quite a\nbit as of 2019/2020.", "start": 2257.76, "duration": 3.04, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2019/2020"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Rainforest Alliance, an NGO\noperating in 70 countries,", "start": 2272.64, "duration": 4.08, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "Rainforest Alliance"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "70"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The new Supply Chain Act, which\nwill take effect starting in 2023,", "start": 2297.08, "duration": 4.64, "ents": [{"label_": "PRODUCT", "text": "Supply Chain Act"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "2023"}], "sentiment": 0.06818181818181818}, {"text": "We meet three women who speak openly", "start": 2341.4, "duration": 2.04, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "20 cents a bag\ninstead of only 10.", "start": 2368.44, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "MONEY", "text": "20 cents"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "only 10"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "This year I have done three or four\ninspections in the state of S\u00e3o Paulo,", "start": 2484.68, "duration": 4.16, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "This year"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "four"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "S\u00e3o Paulo"}], "sentiment": 0.0}], "VIDEO_ID": "9o5lqEzz3Bo", "VIDEO_DATA": [{"videoId": "9o5lqEzz3Bo", "channelId": "UCW39zufHfsuGgpLviKh297Q", "description": "Brazil is the world's top supplier of orange juice. But accusations abound of exploitation and poor working conditions for laborers.", "title": "The hidden cost of orange juice | DW Documentary", "publishedAt": "2022-09-12T16:00:09Z"}]}